Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.60,0:00:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉 肚子饿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.22,0:00:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要不要吃点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.88,0:00:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果那样我去买
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.15,0:00:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吉芙提尔也可以吃东西的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.08,0:00:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃 你在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.86,0:00:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.10,0:00:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要喝茶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.47,0:00:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃 我现在更想吃饭…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.27,0:00:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}气氛好尴尬
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(770,0)\pos(624,568)}回到半天前
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.90,0:02:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}从今天开始你要和艾拉一起住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.02,0:02:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一起住是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.61,0:02:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们一般规定搭档的执行者和观测者一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.15,0:02:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.88,0:02:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没错 我也是和康孝住在同一个屋檐下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.43,0:02:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过他平常很少回来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉住在我们公司的宿舍里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.14,0:02:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你也搬到那边去好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我和艾拉一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.98,0:03:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么时候开始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.34,0:03:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果可以的话就今天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.89,0:03:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.46,0:03:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的是今天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}再怎么说也有点太仓促了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.11,0:03:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那样不会很糟糕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.02,0:03:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}而且那种规定…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司的那个淫荡的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以外行人真的是糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.91,0:03:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么 你吃醋了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.50,0:03:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我看上去是那样吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.44,0:03:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛 我能理解你担心什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}默默守护着她就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.30,0:03:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天工作结束之后我带你去宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.28,0:03:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}…嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.35,0:03:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}宿舍挺大的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.51,0:03:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}SAI公司全部的部门都有人住在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:03:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.08,0:04:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}满和塞克在旁边的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.54,0:04:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}绘瑠则在他们的旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.22,0:04:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我进了艾拉的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.10,0:04:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天开始…我要在这里…和艾拉同居
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.13,0:04:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在房间里的东西请随意使用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.79,0:04:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不需要顾忌我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦…那是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂…忽然间怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs22\c&H484747&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fad(0,150)\pos(942,10)}总算和香月和好了。\N\N结果又是在照顾醉醺醺的香月时\N\N筋疲力尽然后和好了\N\N嘛不管怎样也比一直吵架要好\N\N可是香月明明不怎么会喝酒还喝那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.64,0:04:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}四月十号天气晴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.98,0:05:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天和香月吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.59,0:05:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她生气的时候真的非常的可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那样的话可嫁不出去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.39,0:05:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}日记里和平时简直就是两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是搞不懂女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.03,0:05:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在看什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.71,0:05:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小司早安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.07,0:05:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.82,0:05:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等等…那不是艾拉的日记吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.23,0:05:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么司会拿着它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你该不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.58,0:05:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不不 这是个误会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.03,0:05:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么误会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.65,0:05:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以我才一直反对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.98,0:05:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你这小子图谋着对艾拉做些下流的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没有图谋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.94,0:05:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\move(640,664,640,710,190,690)}有和女生交往的经验吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.31,0:05:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然是没经验啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我还什么都没说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.26,0:05:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让这样的你和艾拉同居
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.92,0:05:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我一点都不觉得你可以保持理性
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.76,0:05:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}满有资格说别人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.56,0:06:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}塞…塞克？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.29,0:06:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那句话是什么意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.33,0:06:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小满虽然那样说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.92,0:06:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是我可是支持小司的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}支持？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.38,0:06:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}YES
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,0:06:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以为了将你和艾拉的同居生活变成玫瑰色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.20,0:06:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我来教你秘藏的诀窍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.91,0:06:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其名曰「幸运色狼大作战」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拿出你的笔记 这里考试会考哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.63,0:06:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.88,0:06:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听好了 首先小艾拉洗澡的时候是好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.27,0:06:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要装作没有注意到打开门
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.16,0:06:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样在突然邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}发出「呀 讨厌」的悲鸣的同时也会脸红心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.20,0:06:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这才是恋爱喜剧的王道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}绘瑠 你在说什么傻话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.41,0:06:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司你也别在这里做笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.57,0:06:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小满你也太激动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.27,0:06:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总之 你要是敢对艾拉做了一点点奇怪的事的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.84,0:06:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看我把你从宿舍里揍出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.09,0:07:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.64,0:07:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要说什么奇怪的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}问题根本就不可能到那一步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.37,0:07:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛 我可是好好的传授给你作战方案了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.51,0:07:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然有点不好意思提回报
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.39,0:07:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}下次能不能替我拜托小艾拉一点事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能不能让小艾拉穿这个看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.14,0:07:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这…难道是自己做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.74,0:07:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我觉得会很合身呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是小艾拉从来不接受别人的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.53,0:07:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不知道失败了多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要装作没有注意到打开门
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.06,0:07:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}打开门…打开门…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不行不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没看到 我什么都没看到！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.02,0:08:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被讨厌了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.77,0:08:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你很没精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}宿舍生活发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.57,0:08:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我又弄不明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.46,0:08:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 还想要喝的话告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.72,0:08:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也就是只有在宿舍里被完全无视吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.78,0:08:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样的话 就来锻炼肌肉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.16,0:08:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}锻炼肌肉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.33,0:08:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要表现出你是一个可靠的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.98,0:08:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}顺利的话 她可能就会敞开心扉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:08:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.99,0:09:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}原来如此 啊哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉 那个啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.78,0:09:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然回到房间就不跟我说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.55,0:09:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}既然这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还没结束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.06,0:09:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉 如果有力气活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.92,0:09:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}尽管告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.68,0:09:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我擦 刚才好像有很大的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.45,0:09:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们在闹什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.39,0:10:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}满说司是个变态哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.88,0:10:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要用这些体育系的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.36,0:10:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要好好的交流才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}课长他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}无论如何白天有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}前些日子是不是被女儿说很恶心然后痛哭流涕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}交流的时间本来就有限
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.23,0:10:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还有似乎有被说「不要把内衣一起洗哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.14,0:10:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}不管多么的累也要挤出一点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.62,0:10:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听好了 司君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.09,0:10:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听我说的就没有问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.62,0:10:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.64,0:10:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最近会做料理的男人似乎很受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.98,0:10:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉 很快就要做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.89,0:10:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来尝尝我的手艺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.30,0:10:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没关系 虽然我是第一次做菜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.49,0:10:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是会按照教程来做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.93,0:10:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在加上点白兰地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么 真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.74,0:10:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 我昨天叫你不要闹了不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.41,0:10:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么停下这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.88,0:11:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}停下…冷死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.81,0:11:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总之…停
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.39,0:11:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 请你不要气馁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}康斯坦斯 如果是你这种时候怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.08,0:11:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我吗 是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.30,0:11:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对待女士要表现的绅士一些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.16,0:11:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}特别是艾拉经常摔倒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.38,0:11:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好好做一个护花使者不是很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.60,0:11:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}踩到那个可能会摔倒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉 稍微等下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.45,0:11:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我先把那个收拾了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.21,0:11:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那么送她一束花怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:11:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉 占用一点时间可以吗
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.64,0:12:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉 快逃 这里交给我解决
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.12,0:12:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 你在乱闹什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.57,0:12:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样的话 为了解开结界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.62,0:12:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要用和平时不同的打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}晚上好啊 艾拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.87,0:12:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这身装扮怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是我从绘瑠那里借过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.39,0:12:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当世界充满黑暗的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.76,0:12:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我降临到这个世界…好疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.39,0:12:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}降临…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.39,0:12:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 别太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}降临了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我听说了你的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:12:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司还不懂得如何和女性相处
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:13:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这也是没办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我在这告诉你一个珍藏的秘籍怎样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.24,0:13:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}秘籍？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.83,0:13:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一定要强行推倒她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.22,0:13:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是一定要完美地伪装成事故
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}女人就是需要借口的生物啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.93,0:13:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吶 艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.07,0:13:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要喝茶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,0:13:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}危险
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.48,0:13:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一定要强行推倒她的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.82,0:13:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}的哦…的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.10,0:14:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你啊 每天晚上都搞什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.55,0:14:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.07,0:14:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和女人一起生活真的是很艰难呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.53,0:14:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没能和艾拉好好相处呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.17,0:14:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.35,0:14:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这不是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉在私下的场合不管是对谁都是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.10,0:14:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到底原因是什么 完全搞不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那孩子 可能想保持身为一个机器的状态吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你明天是休息日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.31,0:14:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要不要把艾拉带到外面去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.83,0:14:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算我邀请 她也会被拒绝的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.61,0:14:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不行的话就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.76,0:15:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和工作的时候一样的感觉对待她就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没必要勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.11,0:15:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你和艾拉应该很合得来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.45,0:15:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和那孩子一起生活6年的我都这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.83,0:15:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拿出点自信来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.74,0:15:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.72,0:15:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拜托你了 只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.97,0:15:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可不要对艾拉暗送秋波哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.70,0:15:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.46,0:15:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明天 我想一直和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.64,0:15:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 不对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.04,0:15:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明天 一起去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.14,0:15:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么感觉好轻浮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.07,0:15:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}把你明天的时间交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.23,0:15:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太装模作样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.89,0:15:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 你不也去上个厕所吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.05,0:15:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 不 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.21,0:15:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉 明天…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.50,0:15:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.48,0:15:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对了 我想给那些在工作中照顾我们的人道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.96,0:16:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为要买些礼物 所以想请你陪我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.99,0:16:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不行的话就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.24,0:16:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.10,0:16:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.46,0:16:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能邀请到是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是现在要怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.35,0:16:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么要穿制服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难道是没有私服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.24,0:16:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在家穿的衣服的话是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.83,0:16:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.88,0:16:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这种的怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.83,0:16:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}稍微试穿一下看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.85,0:16:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我来试穿？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.94,0:16:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.81,0:16:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.69,0:16:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 那个…就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.92,0:16:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想送礼物的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.65,0:16:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和艾拉身形很相似
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.01,0:16:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司…司
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.20,0:16:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遇到麻烦事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.52,0:17:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我进来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.43,0:17:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.45,0:17:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这位客人 发生什么事了吗
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.96,0:17:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}赔偿后原谅我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.21,0:17:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又拖了司的后腿了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别在意 衣服就下次再买吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对不起 我没帮上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.01,0:17:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之前我们在这里见过面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.09,0:17:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.62,0:17:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.85,0:17:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那时候你是来买什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.53,0:17:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:17:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香草的专卖店啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.17,0:18:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你经常来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.40,0:18:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}偶尔会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.69,0:18:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要买点什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.19,0:18:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.47,0:18:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对…对了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.55,0:18:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不送衣服作礼物了 就送香草吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.08,0:18:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可以给我推荐一些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.22,0:18:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你想要哪种类型的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.12,0:18:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就选艾拉你最喜欢的就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.97,0:18:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这和我的兴趣无关
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.13,0:18:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}告诉我那是个怎样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.49,0:18:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我根据那个给你推荐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.47,0:18:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个… 那个人不怎么爱说话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.52,0:18:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在家里经常发呆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.13,0:18:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吃的也很少
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.76,0:18:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不如说我也不知道她到底吃不吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.93,0:18:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还有她好像对喜欢的东西非常执着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.59,0:18:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是个麻烦的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.86,0:18:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没…没那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.18,0:18:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是 我大致了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.60,0:18:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H575960&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord0\fs25\pos(243,373)\frx336\fry26\frz22.522}胡椒薄荷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.86,0:18:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你还戴眼镜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.07,0:19:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老花眼？！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢你 买到好东西了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.93,0:19:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能帮上忙就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.03,0:19:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是游乐园啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要过去看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.48,0:19:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是有好多人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.78,0:19:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 我有个问题要问你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.48,0:19:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明礼物都买好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.18,0:19:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么还要来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.32,0:19:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.03,0:19:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其实 我想感谢的那个人就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.35,0:19:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}麻烦的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.28,0:19:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我没那么觉得 没有没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.26,0:19:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么给我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.48,0:19:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}作为成为搭档的纪念品…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.26,0:19:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这种理由行不行呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.81,0:19:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算是搭档 也只不过是工作上的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.62,0:19:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别那么说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.51,0:20:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想和今天一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.08,0:20:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在个人生活上也和艾拉一起留下很多美好的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回忆……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.72,0:20:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.79,0:20:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}错误
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.79,0:20:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果是这样的话 就不能继续前行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.15,0:20:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为我不是为了能够在游乐园里玩耍 而被制造出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.86,0:20:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.08,0:20:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.16,0:20:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.80,0:21:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在我来之前 艾拉一直是那样一个人的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.41,0:21:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是小艾拉从来不接受别人的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.46,0:21:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.83,0:21:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是我在游乐园买来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.69,0:21:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可以收下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不想要的话 等等扔掉也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.85,0:21:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 对不起 刚才我先回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.21,0:21:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我才是 强行邀请你去 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.24,0:21:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能帮我用这个泡茶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.74,0:22:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.04,0:22:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真好喝
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
